Titolo: Samorost 3

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Samorost 3 is a puzzle point-and-click adventure game developed by Amanita Design. It is the third video game title in the Samorost series and the sequel to Samorost 2. It is the first game in the series that is full-length and with high-definition graphics. The story takes place across five planets and four moons. The game was originally scheduled for 2015.Samorost 3 has sold over 300,000 units as of February 2017.